      "updated": 1773132384539,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "I want to buy running shoes, but I am not sure which brand or model is suitable for my feet and\nrunning style. Running shoes are often expensive, so I cannot afford to buy multiple pairs just to try\nthem. Therefore, I would like to try different running shoes before making a final purchase decision.",
