      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "I want to buy running shoes, but I am not sure which brand or model is suitable for my feet and running style. Running shoes are often expensive, so I cannot afford to buy multiple pairs just to try them. Therefore, I would like to try different running shoes before making a final purchase decision.",
